---
title: Mediterranean Meatball Pitas with Tomato, Cucumber & Dill-Yogurt Sauce
description: We’ve ditched the marinara sauce and rolls in this meatball sandwich for tangy yogurt sauce and soft, pillowy pitas! You’ll roast up a sheet of savory Mediterranean spiced beef meatballs, load them into warm pitas with crunchy cucumber-tomato salad, then drizzle with creamy yogurt-dill sauce for a mouthwatering meal in a quick 20 minutes.
